   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give 300 Zimbabwean Children an Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will give 300 rural Zimbabwean children a quality education and a brighter future. Breakfast, Masuwe and Sekebelo Primary Schools are severely under-resourced. Full classroms where teachers often instruct multiple grades in the same classroom. Basic education materials are severely lacking. Parents cannot afford to pay school fees and the few teachers often work unpaid for months.  Help us provide the support and basic necessities to give these children an education - and a future.</narrative>
  </description>
